@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_amigng(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.exp(0.54))
    tmp = 0.38
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.exp((v0 + 0.68 - v2 + 0.85)))
    v1 = v2
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.exp((tmp + 0.53 + v0 + 0.13)))
    tmp = v2
    v2 = ((0.21 * wp.abs(v0 + 0.65)) / (wp.exp(v0 + 0.52) * tmp))
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.abs(v1))
    data[tid] = v0
